(460,11,1,'SINGLE','MEDIUM','并行进位加法器中，进位产生函数Gi和进位传递函数Pi分别是？','[{"key": "A", "value": "Gi=AiBi, Pi=Ai+Bi"}, {"key": "B", "value": "Gi=AiBi, Pi=Ai xor Bi"}, {"key": "C", "value": "Gi=Ai+Bi, Pi=AiBi"}, {"key": "D", "value": "Gi=Ai xor Bi, Pi=AiBi"}]','B','Gi=AiBi（本位产生进位），Pi=Ai xor Bi（传递低位进位）。',2018),
